title: The Peter Schiff Show - 2011 Mar 03 TH [sebaygo1]

The Peter Schiff Show
Thursday, 03 March 2011


[sebaygo1]


Thursday's guest is Vox Day, publisher of the popular Vox Popoli blog & author of the book "Return of the Great Depression," on Ben Bernanke's confidence spiking energy problems is no big deal, and Day's belief that deflation is a greater present threat than inflation.
